{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"hvZDIGOc5JxRs3IIwQAij","title":"Milestones","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[],"anchors":{"overall-requirements":{"type":"header","text":"Overall Requirements","value":"overall-requirements","line":8,"column":0},"confirmation-1st-year":{"type":"header","text":"Confirmation (1st year)","value":"confirmation-1st-year","line":12,"column":0},"oral-presentation":{"type":"header","text":"Oral Presentation","value":"oral-presentation","line":18,"column":0},"written-submission":{"type":"header","text":"Written Submission","value":"written-submission","line":23,"column":0},"progress-review-2nd-year":{"type":"header","text":"Progress Review (2nd Year)","value":"progress-review-2nd-year","line":38,"column":0},"oral-presentation-1":{"type":"header","text":"Oral Presentation","value":"oral-presentation-1","line":40,"column":0},"written-submission-1":{"type":"header","text":"Written Submission","value":"written-submission-1","line":48,"column":0},"final-review-3rd-year-pre-submission":{"type":"header","text":"Final Review (3rd year, pre-submission!)","value":"final-review-3rd-year-pre-submission","line":62,"column":0},"oral-presentation-2":{"type":"header","text":"Oral Presentation","value":"oral-presentation-2","line":64,"column":0},"written-submission-2":{"type":"header","text":"Written Submission","value":"written-submission-2","line":70,"column":0}},"fname":"Thesis.milestones","updated":1637710858485,"created":1637710027186,"parent":"1ruiVSk3lFpEOUNqPnYti","children":[],"data":{},"contentHash":"001f155e6827f0d440c3d02986057914","custom":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"milestones\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#milestones\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Milestones</h1>\n<h2 id=\"overall-requirements\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#overall-requirements\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Overall Requirements</h2>\n<p>3 papers, ideally published by the end of the PhD.</p>\n<h2 id=\"confirmation-1st-year\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#confirmation-1st-year\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Confirmation (1st year)</h2>\n<p>[x] Get 70 in BEX6500</p>\n<p>[x] Get 70 in BEX6510</p>\n<h3 id=\"oral-presentation\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#oral-presentation\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Oral Presentation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>20 minutes presentation in open forum</li>\n<li>Research undertaken to date </li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"written-submission\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#written-submission\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Written Submission</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>Title of Thesis</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Background and Motivation for the research questions being addressed in the thesis</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Overview of thesis</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Brief detail of proposed content of all chapters</li>\n<li>Description of theoretical and conceptual framework that underlies thesis</li>\n<li>procedures that are to be used in addressing the research questions</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Timetable for completing thesis and statement of progress to date</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Bibliography of reference that appear in the report</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>This report must be submitted 1 week prior to the actual panel date</p>\n<h2 id=\"progress-review-2nd-year\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#progress-review-2nd-year\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Progress Review (2nd Year)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"oral-presentation-1\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#oral-presentation-1\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Oral Presentation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>30 minutes presentation</li>\n<li>Explores research undertaken to date</li>\n<li>Anticipated future direction of program</li>\n<li>Describe in detail, at least one element of the research program</li>\n<li>Content must be distinct from confirmation</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"written-submission-1\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#written-submission-1\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Written Submission</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Length is flexible</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>Title</li>\n<li>Brief overview of findings to data</li>\n<li>Proposed thesis structure</li>\n<li>More detailed explanation of an element (e.g. chapter) that was presented orally</li>\n<li>Timetable for completing the thesis + detailed statement of progress towards this work plan</li>\n<li>Identification of any potential difficulties that could impede progress</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Any papers that are working/submitted/accepted are also to be submitted</p>\n<p>If this paper is related to the element that was presented, requirement 4 is not needed</p>\n<h2 id=\"final-review-3rd-year-pre-submission\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#final-review-3rd-year-pre-submission\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Final Review (3rd year, pre-submission!)</h2>\n<h3 id=\"oral-presentation-2\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#oral-presentation-2\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Oral Presentation</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Full Length public seminar</li>\n</ul>\n<ol>\n<li>Summary of thesis</li>\n<li>Describes in detail, at least one element of the program</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"written-submission-2\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading\" href=\"#written-submission-2\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><use xlink:href=\"#svg-link\"></use></svg></a>Written Submission</h3>\n<p>Length is flexible</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Title of Thesis</li>\n<li>Overview of Thesis</li>\n<li>Proposed Thesis structure</li>\n<li>More detailed explanation of the element presented orally</li>\n<li>Timetable for completing the thesis</li>\n<li>Identification of any perceived difficulties that could impede completion of project according to work plan</li>\n</ol>","noteIndex":{"id":"PhD","title":"PhD Homepage","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"roadmap","alias":"roadmap","position":{"start":{"line":12,"column":1,"offset":451},"end":{"line":12,"column":12,"offset":462},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"roadmap"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"Meeting","alias":"Meeting","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":464},"end":{"line":14,"column":12,"offset":475},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"Meeting"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"PhD","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"TODO","alias":"TODO","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":477},"end":{"line":16,"column":9,"offset":485},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"TODO"}}],"anchors":{"quick-links":{"type":"header","text":"Quick Links","value":"quick-links","line":17,"column":0}},"fname":"root","updated":1637563604861,"created":1595961348801,"parent":null,"children":["t58wEmhAtf1GlHmO","Wnsnl9Ff8hLGapBoL37BK","CQTUwoXQNcd0Y7la7IaAn","9s2d4L1UHWFWCdtORYT2Q","AiXOWFsdvi3BPZxcUMjIi","MsmFdXyWfizd5g8GGcObD","MXHvc8bQbNRRVCB0UogRy","T4FN6sDHfA9wxiZ7Dg5WX","jtZSk246bVVDfJy6cdpS1","2qGHFR7CcKOE0Meu7UU6D","qGmGYptDKW2WLwlsu2xJw","GvwoAWaYZxq1czYi3t3k4","ZIDZSAYP9a9L7jYhVMgcz","WOnXV41UlGcOQzEoTZzJU","fhf7Gdr3mhOUG1mU5twC6","AOvKFmg0tBcGmUASXaALX","qDVp6IFHf6FiUdSgxwZMA",